#

Italian Sausage and Peppers

30 min
$12
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyQuickComfort Food

Description

A hearty and flavorful dish of Italian sausage cooked with vibrant bell peppers and onions, perfect for a quick dinner.

Ingredients

  • italian sausage links: 4
  • bell peppers (any color): 2
  • onion: 1
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
